sequenceDiagram
  participant User
  participant CLI as pubdelays slurm workflow
  participant SLURM as sbatch/sacct
  participant FS as Filesystem
  participant Manifest as Per-task manifests

  User->>CLI: slurm workflow --shards 64
  CLI->>SLURM: submit parse array
  SLURM->>FS: write JSONL parse shards
  SLURM->>Manifest: write parse task SQLite rows
  CLI->>SLURM: submit prepare-transform afterok parse
  SLURM->>FS: write transform_inputs.txt
  CLI->>SLURM: submit transform-shards array afterok prepare
  SLURM->>FS: write article shards
  SLURM->>Manifest: write transform task SQLite rows
  CLI->>SLURM: submit aggregate-all afterok transform
  SLURM->>FS: validate shards and write processed outputs
  User->>CLI: manifest collect --input-dir data/manifests/slurm
  CLI->>Manifest: append task rows into pipeline.sqlite
